{"tid":172552,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"窮撚船p，有錢人勿入。","createTime":"2017-03-26T03:39:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-26T04:19:30.000Z","uid":2107,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a2013f5222bfc888a59fa58dd3f042f604f3b34c","tid":172552,"uid":2107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T03:39:32.000Z","msg":"是咁的，呢個星期五，我唔去浦了。夜晚出海。 <br />\n我book 左隻船<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8w78e7P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8w78e7P.jpg&h=d01670bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D97nSF2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD97nSF2.jpg&h=d7175a86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n坐50人的，長80幾呎仲有專車接送<br />\n<br />\n另一隻, 西班牙式木筏 真材實料<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/06wh8s5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F06wh8s5.jpg&h=9c16bd5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/56H1974.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F56H1974.jpg&h=ddeda04f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我中意呢隻多d，夠簡潔 真材實料<br />\n<br />\n重有一隻普通 中式船<br />\n<br />\n搞手會買好多酒 (古綿純 五粮液)<br />\n<br />\n星期五 , 7點屯門碼頭集合<br />\n<br />\n男仔：$100 位<br />\n女仔：Model , 靚女免費。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n普通女仔：唔俾去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n來吧靚女，識d俾得$100去船河的人吧。 <br />\n<br />\np.s. 呢d船河無得賺，搞手只求打個和，大家開開心心玩返晚。"},{"pid":"3afd856caf3ef04713b249325f8da3a1f1b748af","tid":172552,"uid":2107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T03:41:36.000Z","msg":"咁好玩 唔會無人玩下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef114868280db7f2637ff42b0b2e2e8917ec6355","tid":172552,"uid":13816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T03:41:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b37793120f766bf60e47de3e39cd50fa6dd97e26","tid":172552,"uid":2107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s